snippet.title: Mullet MadJack - Official 'Wishlist Now' Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
Mullet MadJack is a first-person fast-paced action shooter developed by Hammer95. Set in an anime-inspired future where humans must get a dopamine rush every 10 seconds, players must kill in quick succession to get the best time reaching the top of the tower. Mullet MadJack is launching soon for PC with the ability to wishlist on Steam being available now.

#MulletMadJack
